dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.vnrole.Administrator
dataStructure.description:
This is an abstract base class for defining different types of administration roles. An Administrator is a PartyRole who manages and maintains Resources and Services. Subclasses of this class administer specific types of Resources and Services. In general, an Administrator can configure and provision many more features and functions of a Resource or a Service than a Technician can.

This entity is abstract

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: Administrator
